GameBoard - Class in com.example.dmscoursework.View.Board
The GameBoard class makes the game board on which the game is played.
GameBoard(StartController) - Constructor for class com.example.dmscoursework.View.Board.GameBoard
Constructs a game board using the information passed to it from the startController such as the theme, the username of the player and the stage that the gameBoard needs to be placed on.
